name: Priapus A. Tarou (Mentaiko)
description:
This LoRA is trained on Priapus A. Tarou (プリアポス・A・太郎), the Greek god of fertility and male genitalia who was tasked with making all human males homosexual, first appearing in Mentaiko's doujinshi series Priapus, and later the video game GYEE.

The dataset is 52 pics, including doujinshi covers, mentaiko's illustrations, GYEE's official pictures, and some fanarts.

Base model is NAI, but should work on other NAI-based model too. I tested it on AOM2-7thV3_C_40, AOM3, Ally's Mix III, Snovel. It works well with style LoRA too.

Join us in the #men-only channel on Unstable Diffusion Discord server, for lively discussion of how to make good men with Stable Diffusion. You can find my style LoRAs, along with other men-focused LoRAs made by other amazing people, in the #LoRa thread of this channel.
